  "prompt": "Which English songs would you like to listen to again and again without getting bored?",
  "response": "There are countless English songs that people find themselves listening to on repeat without getting bored! Here are some timeless and universally beloved tracks across different genres that have stood the test of time:\n\n### **Pop Classics:**\n1. **\"Bohemian Rhapsody\" - Queen**  \n2. **\"Billie Jean\" - Michael Jackson**  \n3. **\"Rolling in the Deep\" - Adele**  \n4. **\"Shape of You\" - Ed Sheeran**  \n5. **\"Uptown Funk\" - Mark Ronson ft. Bruno Mars**  \n\n### **Rock Anthems:**\n1. **\"Hotel California\" - Eagles**  \n2. **\"Stairway to Heaven\" - Led Zeppelin**  \n3. **\"Smells Like Teen Spirit\" - Nirvana**  \n4. **\"Sweet Child o' Mine\" - Guns N' Roses**  \n5. **\"Livin' on a Prayer\" - Bon Jovi**  \n\n### **R&B/Soul Favorites:**\n1. **\"Ain't No Sunshine\" - Bill Withers**  \n2. **\"I Will Always Love You\" - Whitney Houston**  \n3. **\"Blame It on the Boogie\" - The Jacksons**  \n4. **\"Redemption Song\" - Bob Marley**  \n5. **\"Let's Stay Together\" - Al Green**  \n\n### **Hip-Hop/Rap Hits:**\n1. **\"Lose Yourself\" - Eminem**  \n2. **\"Juicy\" - The Notorious B.I.G.**  \n3. **\"Sicko Mode\" - Travis Scott**  \n4. **\"Hotline Bling\" - Drake**  \n5. **\"Empire State of Mind\" - Jay-Z ft. Alicia Keys**  \n\n### **Indie/Alternative Gems:**\n1. **\"Mr. Brightside\" - The Killers**  \n2. **\"Take Me Out\" - Franz Ferdinand**  \n3. **\"Float On\" - Modest Mouse**  \n4. **\"Skinny Love\" - Bon Iver**  \n5. **\"Somebody That I Used to Know\" - Gotye ft. Kimbra**  \n\n### **EDM/Pop Anthems:**\n1. **\"Titanium\" - David Guetta ft. Sia**  \n2. **\"Wake Me Up\" - Avicii**  \n3. **\"Lean On\" - Major Lazer & DJ Snake ft. M\u00d8**  \n4. **\"Don't You Worry Child\" - Swedish House Mafia**  \n5. **\"Closer\" - The Chainsmokers ft. Halsey**  \n\n### **Feel-Good Classics:**\n1. **\"Don't Stop Believin'\" - Journey**  \n2. **\"Dancing Queen\" - ABBA**  \n3. **\"I Gotta Feeling\" - The Black Eyed Peas**  \n4. **\"All Star\" - Smash Mouth**  \n5. **\"Happy\" - Pharrell Williams**  \n\nThese songs are iconic for their catchy melodies, meaningful lyrics, or unforgettable beats, making them perfect for repeated listening! What\u2019s your favorite genre?",
